snippet.title: Best VGM 1004 - Spyro : A Hero's Tail - Cloudy Domain
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1911 - https://youtu.be/nK-IjRF-hs4

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS2 / Xbox / Gamecube
Spyro : A Hero's Tail (2004)
Cloudy Domain
Guy Cockcroft & Steve Duckworth
